Class Drug

    java.io.Serializable

    @Entity(name="Drug")
public class Drug
extends BaseEntity
    The Drug class is a representation of a medication. It contains the Drug name, its GTIN (Global Trade Item Number) and a description. Each Drug can be assigned to several Patients (prescription).
